abar-duka-bupati-manokwari-demas-paulus-mandacan-meninggal Kabar Duka: Bupati Manokwari Demas Paulus Mandacan Meninggal] {{in lang|id}}</ref>\n*[[Ronan O'Rahilly]], 79, Irish businessman, founder of [[Radio Caroline]], vascular dementia.<ref>[https://radiotoday.ie/2020/04/radio-caroline-founder-ronan-orahilly-has-died/ Radio Caroline founder Ronan O\u2019Rahilly has died]</ref>\n*[[Hezakiah Oshutapik]], 63, Canadian politician, [[Legislative Assembly of Nunavut|MLA]] (2011\u20132013).<ref>[https://nunatsiaq.com/stories/article/pangnirtung-mayor-hezakiah-oshutapik-passed-away-over-the-weekend/ Pangnirtung Mayor Hezakiah Oshutapik passes away]</ref> (death announced on this date)\n*[[Gabriel Retes]], 73, Mexican film director (''[[Paper Flowers (1977 film)|Paper Flowers]]'', ''[[Broken Flag]]'', ''[[A Sweet Scent of Death]]'').<ref>[https://www.infobae.com/america/entretenimiento/2020/04/20/murio-el-cineasta-gabriel-retes-director-de-el-bulto/ Muri\u00f3 el cineasta Gabriel Retes, director de \u201cEl Bulto\u201d] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*[[Manjeet Singh Riyat]], 52, British emergency care consultant, COVID-19.<ref>[https://www.derbytelegraph.co.uk/news/derby-news/royal-derby-hospital-consultant-dad-4063114 Royal Derby Hospital consultant and dad-of-two dies after contracting coronavirus]</ref>\n*{{ill|Josep Sala Ma\u00f1\u00e9|es}}, 82, Spanish [[Castell|casteller]], founder of [[Castellers de Barcelona]], COVID-19.<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/barcelona/20200421/muere-josep-sala-mane-fundador-castellers-barcelona-7935157 Muere el fundador de los Castellers de Barcelona, Josep Sala, por coronavirus] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*[[Innokentiy Samokhvalov]], 22, Russian footballer ([[FC Lokomotiv Moscow]], [[FC Kazanka Moscow]]), heart failure.<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/football/2020/apr/20/lokomotiv-moscow-player-dies-aged-22-after-falling-ill-in-home-training-session Lokomotiv Moscow player dies aged 22 after falling ill in home training session]</ref>\n*[[Rudra